            <ul>
                <li>You're already using it on your site and every browser understands it</li>
                <li>Largest ecosystem in the world - the best AI tools were trained on it</li>
                <li>AI implementations are asynchronous by nature - that's a real problem with PHP</li>
                <li><span class="yellow">Node is enough - no extra DB, no Apache, no Nginx, runs easily on any machine</span></li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section data-background="content/images/vibe-coding-start/vibe-coding-start-en-astro.jpg" data-background-repeat="no-repeat" data-background-size="contain" data-background-position="center top">
        </section>

