            <h2>02 - Real Benefits</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Your site loads in under 1 second - Google ranks it higher</li>
                <li>Data can be exported statically and dropped straight into the page</li>
                <li>Hosting costs nothing, e.g. GitHub Pages</li>
                <li><span class="yellow">Independent of the CMS implementation</span></li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section data-background="content/images/vibe-coding-start/vibe-coding-start-en-benefits.jpg" data-background-repeat="no-repeat" data-background-size="contain" data-background-position="center top">
