            <h2>03 - Rules for AI Code</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Without rules, every AI session builds differently - chaos nobody understands</li>
                <li>With rules, the AI builds exactly the way you want - same quality, every time</li>
                <li>Our guidelines come from real projects with real mistakes</li>
                <li><span class="yellow">"You are absolutely right" never happens again</span></li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section data-background="content/images/vibe-coding-start/vibe-coding-start-en-rules.jpg" data-background-repeat="no-repeat" data-background-size="contain" data-background-position="center top">
        </section>

