            <ul>
                <li>Every change is tested automatically before it goes live</li>
                <li><span class="yellow">Broken is hell</span> - defective pages never go live</li>
                <li>Later always works - better to wait than hot-fix</li>
                <li>Deploy with one click - no FTP, no manual copying, multiple times a day</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

